    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/3a3fa5c6989f449320526c1747683224.poster.avif?t=1770568929\" width=1170 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/3a3fa5c6989f449320526c1747683224.webm?t=1770568929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/3a3fa5c6989f449320526c1747683224.mp4?t=1770568929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/b2f5df021b0374d96dee614c9bce0b92.avif?t=1770568929\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >勤杂工马利克接到任务，要整修位于德国柏林的一间旧公寓，他的女儿迪拉拉也来帮忙。在大规模的翻修工作过程中，迪拉拉不断深入挖掘这间公寓的历史。昔日的遗物既是公寓住户曾经的伙伴，也是无声的见证人。每次有新的发现，马利克都会把这段过去冒险痕迹背后的故事讲给女儿听——故事的类型和氛围各不相同，也有着各色鲜活的角色，但不变的是，它们都发生在这四面墙内。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/8f2056e4ca7a8fae16db58ad0a1336a7.poster.avif?t=1770568929\" width=1170 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/8f2056e4ca7a8fae16db58ad0a1336a7.webm?t=1770568929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/8f2056e4ca7a8fae16db58ad0a1336a7.mp4?t=1770568929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/c285a9dd3ef33102a26cc023ad45549f.avif?t=1770568929\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满秘密的过往：</strong>发现遗物和痕迹，揭晓公寓及其住户的历史。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独一无二的剧情：</strong>深入挖掘动人的小故事，每个新故事都有独特的曲折玩法。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美丽清爽的画风：</strong>探索精美细致的 3D 环境，感受丰富多彩的漫画审美。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不断变迁的柏林：</strong>体验一座缤纷城市独特的历史背景及其动荡不安的过去。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280430/extras/7f2289d1c964ee4ddedba65fdfe3825a.avif?t=1770568929\" width=1200 height=400 /></span> </p>",
